					<div class="company-info">
							<img class="logo" src="https://s.dou.ua/CACHE/images/img/static/companies/logo-dou_nvwULN9/812d79f6260e65fb3d5abc527c010bf2.png" srcset="https://s.dou.ua/CACHE/images/img/static/companies/logo-dou_nvwULN9/56cf3eed165c62d1cabd8c751397dcc6.png 1.1x" alt="Codemotion">

						<h1 class="g-h2">
							Codemotion


						</h1>

								81...200 специалистов

								<div class="offices">
Киев, Ужгород, Тбилиси (Грузия)								</div>

