				<span class="prof">
						--
				</span>


				<a class="comment-link" href="#38104">26 декабря 2018 10:56</a>
			</div>

		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<p>Been working here for some time now. Ive worked for a&nbsp;lot of&nbsp;companies before this one, but this is&nbsp;the best experience i&nbsp;had so&nbsp;far. The office is&nbsp;nice and cozy, there are a&nbsp;lot of&nbsp;nice things that can help you relax during the day if&nbsp;you get tired. You can go&nbsp;play some ping-pong or&nbsp;go&nbsp;play some PS4. Its up&nbsp;to&nbsp;you how you want to&nbsp;relax. The schedule is&nbsp;very flexible and the people here are nice. There is&nbsp;not much to&nbsp;add here except that this is&nbsp;an&nbsp;amazing company and&nbsp;I think this company is&nbsp;like a&nbsp;unicorn that everyone is&nbsp;looking for but it&nbsp;actually exists :)</p>
		</div>

				<div class="bottom-line">
						<a class="review-link" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/codemotion/reviews/38104/">Ответить</a>


